OL,3,CRachel Reeves planning #3bn welfare
OL,4,Ccuts in Budget
OL,6,FRachel Reeves will seek to make around
OL,7,F#3 billion of cuts to welfare over the
OL,8,Fnext four years by restricting access
OL,9,Fto sickness benefits, it is understood.
OL,11,FThe Chancellor is expected to commit
OL,12,Fto the previous Tory government's
OL,13,Fplans to save the sum by reforming
OL,14,Fwork capability rules, as first
OL,15,Freported by The Telegraph.
