OL,3,CRachel Reeves planning #3bn welfare
OL,4,Ccuts in Budget
OL,6,FUnder Conservative proposals, welfare
OL,7,Feligibility would have been tightened
OL,8,Fso that around 400,000 more people who
OL,9,Fare signed off long-term would be
OL,10,Fassessed as needing to prepare for
OL,11,Femployment by 2028/29, reducing the
OL,12,Fbenefits bill by an estimated #3
OL,13,Fbillion.
OL,15,FIt is understood that Ms Reeves will
OL,16,Fcommit to the plan to save #3 billion
OL,17,Fover four years, but Work and Pensions
OL,18,FSecretary Liz Kendall will decide how
OL,19,Fthe system will be changed in order to
OL,20,Fachieve this.
