OL,6,FA Government spokesperson said: "We
OL,7,Fhave always said that the Work
OL,8,FCapability Assessment is not working
OL,9,Fand needs to be reformed or replaced
OL,10,Falongside a proper plan to support
OL,11,Fdisabled people to work.
OL,13,F"We will deliver savings through our
OL,14,Fown reforms, including genuine support
OL,15,Fto help disabled people into work."
OL,17,FMs Reeves is looking to raise up to
OL,18,F#40 billion from tax hikes and
OL,19,Fspending cuts in the Budget as the
OL,20,FGovernment seeks to avoid a return to
OL,21,Fausterity.
