OL,3,CRachel Reeves planning #3bn welfare
OL,4,Ccuts in Budget
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer on Thursday faced a
OL,7,FCabinet backlash over the planned
OL,8,Fmeasures, with several ministers
OL,9,Fwriting to the Prime Minister directly
OL,10,Fto express concern about proposals to
OL,11,Freduce their departmental spending by
OL,12,Fas much as 20%.
OL,14,FDowning Street warned that "not every
OL,15,Fdepartment will be able to do
OL,16,Feverything they want to" and "tough
OL,17,Fdecisions" would have to be made.
