OL,4,Ccuts in Budget
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister's official
OL,7,Fspokesman confirmed Sir Keir and Ms
OL,8,FReeves have agreed on the "major
OL,9,Fmeasures" of the Budget, including the
OL,10,F"spending envelope" that sets out
OL,11,Flimits for individual Whitehall
OL,12,Fdepartments.
OL,14,FWhile some spending cuts are all but
OL,15,Finevitable, tax rises are expected to
OL,16,Fform the centrepiece of Ms Reeves'
OL,17,Fplans to fill what the Labour
OL,18,FGovernment calls a "black hole" in the
OL,19,Fpublic finances left behind by its
OL,20,FTory predecessors.
