OL,6,FReports suggest capital gains tax and
OL,7,Finheritance tax are among some of the
OL,8,Flevers the Chancellor will pull to
OL,9,Fraise revenue as she seeks to put the
OL,10,Feconomy on a firmer footing.
OL,12,FThe Budget will be delivered on
OL,13,FOctober 30.
OL,15,FThe Chancellor will hold talks with
OL,16,FCity bosses on Friday at the first
OL,17,Fmeeting of Labour's British
OL,18,Finfrastructure taskforce, as the
OL,19,FGovernment seeks advice on how to
OL,20,Fboost investment in the UK.
