OL,4,Ccuts in Budget
OL,6,FFinance chiefs from HSBC, Lloyds and
OL,7,FM&G will be among those involved in
OL,8,Fthe discussions, which the Treasury
OL,9,Fsays will take place regularly.
OL,11,FMs Reeves said their expertise will be
OL,12,F"invaluable in the weeks and months
OL,13,Fahead" as the Government pursues its
OL,14,F"number one mission to grow the
OL,15,Feconomy and create jobs".
OL,17,FChief Secretary to the Treasury Darren
OL,18,FJones said the taskforce would aim to
OL,19,Fend "the cycle of underinvestment that
OL,20,Fhas plagued our infrastructure systems
OL,21,Ffor over a decade."
